<concept id="concept_E8D43EB4494E41D2AB42D4A89396D1AB"
                xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Installing the Monitoring Service</title>
    <conbody>
        <!-- section>
            <p>CMM Server based on OpenStack Pike / monasca-docker stable pike</p>
        </section -->
        <section>
            <p><ph conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                /> provides a Docker-based installation of the Monitoring Service. Production-ready Docker images are provided for the services that make up the Monitoring Service. Instances of these images will run in separate Docker containers as soon as the installation is successful. </p>
            <p>The installation of the Monitoring Service automatically includes the installation of a Metrics Agents and a Log Agent for monitoring <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/> itself.</p>
        </section>
